            <title>[LU-10612] replay-single test_48 defect causes test failure due to error: No space left on device</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10612</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the following failure is caused by test_48 defect :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Starting mds1: -o rw,user_xattr  /dev/md66 /data/windu03:md66
pdsh@windu-client10: windu03: ssh exited with exit code 1
pdsh@windu-client10: windu03: ssh exited with exit code 1
Started fs1-MDT0000
fail_loc=0x80000216
open(/mnt/fs1/f48.replay-single20) error: No space left on device
total: 0 creates in 0.00 seconds: 0.00 creates/second
 replay-single test_48: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_48 failed with 2 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test is to be fixed so that MDS have a time to discover the OST state, attempt to recover, fail and recover again.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
